# Yarn Berry (Yarn 4) — see https://yarnpkg.com/getting-started/qa#which-files-should-be-gitignored
# Track: .yarn/cache, .yarn/patches, .yarn/plugins, .yarn/releases, .yarn/sdks, .yarn/versions
# Ignore the rest:
.yarn/*
!.yarn/cache
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/sdks
!.yarn/versions
.pnp.*
